@startuml User_Workflow_Sequence
!theme plain
title Complete User Workflow - Document to Exam

actor Educator
participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "FastAPI API" as API
participant "Backend Services" as Services
participant "AI/Vector Systems" as AI

== Document Upload Phase ==
Educator -> Browser: Access ExamCraft AI
Browser -> Frontend: Load application
Frontend --> Browser: Dashboard with upload interface

Educator -> Browser: Drag & drop PDF document
Browser -> Frontend: File upload event
Frontend -> API: Upload document
API -> Services: Process document
Services -> AI: Extract and vectorize content
AI --> Services: Processing complete
Services --> API: Document ready
API --> Frontend: Upload successful
Frontend --> Browser: Show processing status

== Question Generation Phase ==
Educator -> Browser: Navigate to Generate Questions
Browser -> Frontend: Load generation interface
Frontend --> Browser: Show available documents

Educator -> Browser: Select documents and topic
Browser -> Frontend: Form submission
Frontend -> API: Generate questions request
API -> Services: Initiate RAG generation
Services -> AI: Retrieve context and generate
AI --> Services: Generated questions
Services --> API: Questions with sources
API --> Frontend: Question set
Frontend --> Browser: Display questions

== Review and Refine Phase ==
Educator -> Browser: Review generated questions
Browser -> Frontend: Show question editor

alt Question needs editing
  Educator -> Browser: Edit question
  Browser -> Frontend: Update question
  Frontend -> API: Save changes
  API --> Frontend: Updated
else Question is acceptable
  Educator -> Browser: Approve question
  Browser -> Frontend: Mark as approved
end

== Exam Export Phase ==
Educator -> Browser: Request exam export
Browser -> Frontend: Export dialog
Frontend -> API: Generate exam PDF/Word
API -> Services: Create formatted exam
Services --> API: Export file ready
API --> Frontend: Download link
Frontend --> Browser: Trigger download

note right of AI
  RAG system ensures
  questions are based
  on actual document
  content
end note

note right of Services
  All operations are
  logged for audit
  and debugging
end note

@enduml
